comments.body: http.Executor could have been command.Executor... maybe for a future PR? I didn't have time to review this but I had this comment in the previous PR and it was not addressed.

Hi @cnishina ,
Thanks for your comment!
As far as I can see http.Executor is correct, see:

https://github.com/SeleniumHQ/selenium/blob/master/javascript/node/selenium-webdriver/index.js#L641

The code is not super clear in the original selenium-webdriver package. I agree that in a future PR we could clear things up a bit more.
